tsconfig
name of typescript config file
tsconfig.json

tsconfig_include
typescript config: use all .ts files in src
"include": ["src/**/*.ts"]

tsconfig_exclude
typescript config: don't compile files in node_modules
"exclude": ["node_modules"]

tsconfig_extends
typescript config: use base config for node 16
"extends": "@tsconfig/node16/tsconfig.json"

tsconfig_extends_install
typescript setup: yarn install base typescript config for node 16
yarn add --dev @tsconfig/node16

tsconfig_outdir
typescript config: specify destination folder as dist
"compilerOptions": {"outDir": "dist"}

types_node
typescript setup: install node types
yarn add --dev @types/node

yarnglobalremove
yarn uninstall global package a
yarn global remove a

yarnglobaladd
yarn install package a globally
yarn global add a